To appear in JEMS; significant error noted by referee and corrected
  from previous version: Lemma 3.1 wrongly claimed Q_G(\lambda) was M-isotypic;
  see Rk 7.4(ii) in this version

24 pages:improvements to exposition following a referee's report;
  final version,accepted for publication in the Journal of the London
  Mathematical Society

Keywords. speech recognition; natural language processing;
  low-resource language; digital banking; cognitive banking; conversational
  user interface; artificial intelligence (AI); machine learning
